{"type": "article", "id": 26961, "title": "不让人赖床的钟", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-18T07:23:35Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 14, "praise_count": 143, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702171509XcLkMuxY6jI1rpU7.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>早起困难户们，设计师 Snežana Jeremić 推出的这款名为 NEMO 的闹钟或许是你们的福音。闹钟顶部是一个滚球迷宫，为了调整闹铃时间，你必须把球滚到蓝色的小洞中，而关闭闹铃则需要把球滚到红色的小洞里去——哪怕你真的很想再来个回笼觉，等闹铃停止的时候你差不多也因为玩迷宫游戏清醒了不少。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021715075EPynrqR12zKtjdD.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70952381\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702171508bG8M6pNeA0VUliuE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70952381\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702171508FRxZaSOwzcqVAgvm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70952381\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021715097HF2MfKlSODuVT8n.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70952381\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}